						<div class="postbody"><div class="quotetitle">Bregalad wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">However, since that, while Kevtris has worked hard on testing one thousand of cartridge, his format is totally closed for any suggetion, and it doesn't seem that <em>any</em> external idea was even considered to be added/modified.<br /></div>
